<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>167</hymn_number>
<author>Ngama</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Aw ka gamlui khawvel Aigupta,
 Leh ka vaihna lei gimum;
 Na khel lamah lungmuonna leh,
 Van nawpsakna chu ka changtai,
 Na sunga ka guol luihaw sal bang hun suoh in.

[V2]
 Aw, hung zieng in, Lalpa kawm ah,
 A hung pangin Lalpa lamah;
 Lal na sem ding a kiting puou hi,
 Theihtawp a sem dingin nangle chiel na hi.

[V3]
 2. Aw, khawvel a Lalpa loa,
 Sum leh pai tamtak khawlhaw chu;
 A tawpna dingchu thil tiemu,
 Lehkhabu thun ei na hilh chu,
 'A lawpnau cheng pumin,
 Mangthai ding', ti'n ei hilh.

[V4]
 3. Simlei nunnawp ei nung sawn in,
 Gibanga kikhen ding I hi;
 Ka Lalpa ei sapna phu in,
 A nasem din ka kipan tai,
 Chanchin pha thu phuong dingin,
 Guol pha le hawl ka.

[V5]
 4. Aw, van Lal na sem chiet hitiu,
 Alieng nuoi simlei Sapchuom te'n;
 Sietlei gam lienzaw enviel leng,
 Lautha hukdamna chu ngaiin,
 Ei ngak ui &quot;Kei ule ei hung pui un&quot; tiin.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Ka Gam Lui</title>
</song>